thought it was crazy but tried it. When you take cherry pits and crush them, it\par
gives you an almond flavor. I made some pickled sour cherries with the crushed\par
pits in cheesecloth with the pickling liquid and I got this great almondy flavor\par
that went deep inside the cherries.\par
