flavor combinations. The Kobe beef triggered everything. I can\rquote t serve steak at a\par
fish restaurant, but the Kobe was so good I had to find a way to justify it on the\par
menu. I came up with Kobe beef and escalar, with a brown butter that is classic\par
with the fish. The final dish was inspired by having Korean barbecue at a\par
friend\rquote s house, which is when I realized how to bring it together.\par
I wanted another element in the dish because the Kobe, escalar, and brown\par
