strong vegetable like dandelion greens. In the United States, you would put a\par
barbecue sauce on a grilled meat; in Italy, you would use a strong olive oil.\par
\f2\bullet\f1  I use a lighter (e.g., Ligurian, Tuscan) olive oil on lighter meats like veal or fish\par
dishes and pastas. A Ligurian olive is full and bright and is great on a lighter\par
dish.\par
